B.FE=new A.b_(B.Gi,["Home","Skills","Projects","Hi,\nI'm Lucynka\nA Flutter Developer","If you give me a job, I'll give you a paw. \n\nThe Pekingese is a companion dog breed classified in the Japanese Spaniels and Pekingese section. It has a dachshund-type build and does not undergo working trials.\n\nBred in Manchuria, the Pekingese was unknown outside China until the mid-19th century. In China, they were kept as temple dogs. According to Chinese beliefs, their small size helped them chase temple demons, while their brave hearts let them face powerful evil spirits.\n\nAnother legend says Pekingese resulted from a lion and monkey's love\u2014a union blessed by Buddha.","Technical Skills","My projects","Team Projects","Built with: ","View details","\u2709 Mail me","   Top","Copy e-mail","E-mail address copied!","View source on GitHub","Made by: Lucynka \u2014 built with "," Flutter 3.38.4\n\xa9 2025 \u2022 This project is open-source (MIT)","Software Development","Microcontrollers & Embedded Systems","Development Tools & IDEs","Communication Protocols & Interfaces","Single-Board Computers","PCB Design & Circuit Simulation","Prototyping & Assembly","Test & Measurement Equipment","Documentation & Graphics","C","C++","Python","MATLAB","LabVIEW","bash","VHDL","STM32 (HAL/CubeMX)","AVR","ESP32","FreeRTOS basics","STM32CubeIDE","Keil \xb5Vision","Visual Studio Code","Git","CAN","SPI","I2C","UART","Ethernet","BLE","WiFi","NFC","GNSS","GPRS/LTE","Raspberry Pi","Altium Designer","CircuitStudio","PADS","LTspice","PCB assembly","SMD/THT soldering","3D printing","Oscilloscope","Multimeter","Power supplies","Logic analyzers","Frequency counters","Debuggers: ST-Link/SWD","LaTeX","Inkscape","GIMP","Microsoft Office","Pekingese Tracker","App for monitoring Pekingese activity.","The app allows Pekingese owners to track daily activity, walked distances, feeding times, and health behaviors. The project implements a simple statistics system and data export functionality. Designed with small dog breeds in mind, which require regular monitoring of physical activity.","Pekingese Diet Planner","Individual diet planner for Pekingese.","The project focuses on creating optimal nutrition plans for Pekingese, considering age, weight, allergies, and activity level. The app allows recording meals and monitoring the dog's reactions to specific ingredients.","Pekingese Training Hub","Set of exercises and tricks specifically for Pekingese.","The app offers a library of trainings, instructional videos, and weekly challenges tailored to Pekingese - an intelligent breed with a very specific temperament. The project also includes a simple system for assessing training progress.","Pekingese Social Club","Social app for Pekingese owners.","Team project of an application that allows Pekingese owners to share photos, create walking groups, organize events, and contact nearby breeders. The project uses Firebase Authentication and Firestore for community management.","Pekingese Health Companion","Platform for monitoring Pekingese health.","Project created by a team of veterinarians and developers. The app offers a system for reminders about vaccinations, check-up visits, and medication administration. Additionally, it integrates with an external API to fetch information about common diseases for the Pekingese breed and suggest preventive actions."],t.li)
B.Gc={"nav.home":0,"nav.skills":1,"nav.projects":2,greeting:3,biography:4,about_short:5,skills_section:6,projects_my:7,details_button:8,projects_team:9,built_with:10,contact:11,return:12,copy_email:13,email_copied:14,github_source:15,made_by_p1:16,made_by_p2:17,"skills.software":18,"skills.embedded":19,"skills.tools":20,"skills.protocols":21,"skills.sbc":22,"skills.pcb":23,"skills.proto":24,"skills.test":25,"skills.docs":26,"skill.c":27,"skill.cpp":28,"skill.python":29,"skill.matlab":30,"skill.labview":31,"skill.bash":32,"skill.vhdl":33,"skill.stm32_hal_cubemx":34,"skill.avr":35,"skill.esp32":36,"skill.freertos_basics":37,"skill.stm32cubeide":38,"skill.keil_uvision":39,"skill.visual_studio_code":40,"skill.git":41,"skill.can":42,"skill.spi":43,"skill.i2c":44,"skill.uart":45,"skill.ethernet":46,"skill.ble":47,"skill.wifi":48,"skill.nfc":49,"skill.gnss":50,"skill.gprs_lte":51,"skill.raspberry_pi":52,"skill.altium_designer":53,"skill.circuitstudio":54,"skill.pads":55,"skill.ltspice":56,"skill.pcb_assembly":57,"skill.smd_tht_soldering":58,"skill.3d_printing":59,"skill.oscilloscope":60,"skill.multimeter":61,"skill.power_supplies":62,"skill.logic_analyzers":63,"skill.frequency_counters":64,"skill.debuggers_st_link_swd":65,"skill.latex":66,"skill.inkscape":67,"skill.gimp":68,"skill.microsoft_office":69,"project.m1.title":70,"project.m1.subtitle":71,"project.m1.description":72,"project.m2.title":73,"project.m2.subtitle":74,"project.m2.description":75,"project.m3.title":76,"project.m3.subtitle":77,"project.m3.description":78,"project.t1.title":79,"project.t1.subtitle":80,"project.t1.description":81,"project.t2.title":82,"project.t2.subtitle":83,"project.t2.description":84}
B.FK=new A.b_(B.Gc,["Strona g\u0142\xf3wna","Umiej\u0119tno\u015bci","Projekty","Cze\u015b\u0107,\nJestem Lucynka\nFlutter Developer","Jak dasz prac\u0119 to podam \u0142apk\u0119. \n\nPeki\u0144czyk to jedna z ras ps\xf3w nale\u017c\u0105ca do grupy ps\xf3w do towarzystwa, zaklasyfikowana do sekcji spanieli japo\u0144skich i peki\u0144czyk\xf3w. Typ jamnikowaty. Nie podlega pr\xf3bom pracy.\n\nPeki\u0144czyk jest ras\u0105 wyhodowan\u0105 w Mand\u017curii. Do po\u0142owy XIX wieku rasa ta znana by\u0142a wy\u0142\u0105cznie w Chinach, gdzie peki\u0144czyki hodowane by\u0142y jako psy \u015bwi\u0105tynne. Wed\u0142ug chi\u0144skich wierze\u0144 drobna budowa peki\u0144czyka pozwala\u0142a mu \u0142atwo goni\u0107 i chwyta\u0107 pojawiaj\u0105ce si\u0119 w \u015bwi\u0105tyniach demony, a jego waleczne serce - bez trudu stawia\u0107 czo\u0142a nawet najpot\u0119\u017cniejszym z\u0142ym duchom. Inna legenda wspomina, \u017ce peki\u0144czyki mia\u0142y by\u0107 owocem mi\u0142o\u015bci lwa do ma\u0142pki, kt\xf3ry to zwi\u0105zek zosta\u0142 pob\u0142ogos\u0142awiony przez samego Budd\u0119. ","Peki\u0144czyk \u2014 pies do towarzystwa...","Umiej\u0119tno\u015bci","Moje projekty","Zobacz szczeg\xf3\u0142y","Projekty zespo\u0142owe","Wykorzystane technologie: ","\u2709 Napisz do mnie","Powr\xf3t","Kopiuj e-mail","Adres e-mail zosta\u0142 skopiowany!","Zobacz kod na GitHubie","Stworzone przez: Lucynka \u2014 zbudowane z "," Flutter 3.38.4\n\xa9 2025 \u2022 Projekt open-source (MIT)","Programowanie","Mikrokontrolery i systemy wbudowane","Narz\u0119dzia programistyczne i IDE","Protoko\u0142y komunikacyjne i interfejsy","Komputery jednop\u0142ytkowe","Projektowanie PCB i symulacja obwod\xf3w","Prototypowanie i monta\u017c","Sprz\u0119t pomiarowy i diagnostyczny","Dokumentacja i grafika","C","C++","Python","MATLAB","LabVIEW","bash","VHDL","STM32 (HAL/CubeMX)","AVR","ESP32","Podstawy FreeRTOS","STM32CubeIDE","Keil \xb5Vision","Visual Studio Code","Git","CAN","SPI","I2C","UART","Ethernet","BLE","WiFi","NFC","GNSS","GPRS/LTE","Raspberry Pi","Altium Designer","CircuitStudio","PADS","LTspice","Monta\u017c PCB","Lutowanie SMD/THT","Drukowanie 3D","Oscyloskop","Multimetr","Zasilacze","Analizatory logiczne","Liczniki cz\u0119stotliwo\u015bci","Debugery: ST-Link/SWD","LaTeX","Inkscape","GIMP","Microsoft Office","Peki\u0144czyk Tracker","Aplikacja do monitorowania aktywno\u015bci peki\u0144czyka.","Aplikacja umo\u017cliwia w\u0142a\u015bcicielom peki\u0144czyk\xf3w \u015bledzenie dziennej aktywno\u015bci, przebytych spacer\xf3w, godzin karmienia oraz zachowa\u0144 zdrowotnych. W projekcie zaimplementowano prosty system statystyk oraz mo\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107 eksportu danych. Zaprojektowana z my\u015bl\u0105 o ma\u0142ych rasach ps\xf3w, kt\xf3re wymagaj\u0105 regularnej kontroli aktywno\u015bci fizycznej.","Peki\u0144czyk Diet Planner","Indywidualny planer diety peki\u0144czyka.","Projekt skupia si\u0119 na tworzeniu optymalnych plan\xf3w \u017cywieniowych dla peki\u0144czyk\xf3w, z uwzgl\u0119dnieniem wieku, wagi, alergii oraz poziomu aktywno\u015bci. Aplikacja pozwala rejestrowa\u0107 posi\u0142ki i monitorowa\u0107 reakcje psa na poszczeg\xf3lne sk\u0142adniki.","Peki\u0144czyk Training Hub","Zestaw \u0107wicze\u0144 i trick\xf3w specjalnie dla peki\u0144czyk\xf3w.","Aplikacja oferuje bibliotek\u0119 trening\xf3w, film\xf3w instrukta\u017cowych oraz wyzwa\u0144 tygodniowych dostosowanych do peki\u0144czyk\xf3w \u2014 rasy inteligentnej, ale o bardzo specyficznym temperamencie. Projekt zawiera r\xf3wnie\u017c prosty system ocen post\u0119p\xf3w w szkoleniu.","Peki\u0144czyk Social Club","Aplikacja spo\u0142eczno\u015bciowa dla w\u0142a\u015bcicieli peki\u0144czyk\xf3w.","Zespo\u0142owy projekt aplikacji umo\u017cliwiaj\u0105cej w\u0142a\u015bcicielom peki\u0144czyk\xf3w dzielenie si\u0119 zdj\u0119ciami, tworzenie grup spacerowych, organizowanie wydarze\u0144 i kontaktowanie si\u0119 z pobliskimi hodowcami. W projekcie wykorzystano Firebase Authentication oraz Firestore do zarz\u0105dzania spo\u0142eczno\u015bci\u0105.","Peki\u0144czyk Health Companion","Platforma do monitorowania zdrowia peki\u0144czyka.","Projekt tworzony w zespole weterynarzy i programist\xf3w. Aplikacja oferuje system przypomnie\u0144 o szczepieniach, wizytach kontrolnych oraz podawaniu lek\xf3w. Dodatkowo integruje si\u0119 z zewn\u0119trznym API, aby pobiera\u0107 informacje o typowych chorobach dla rasy peki\u0144czyk i sugerowa\u0107 dzia\u0142ania profilaktyczne."],t.li)
